# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# TUX Burger Website — Environment Variables
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to .env and fill in your values.
# NEVER commit your .env file to version control.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────

# No server-side environment variables are required
# for this purely frontend application.
#
# To configure the WhatsApp order button, edit:
#   src/lib/constants.ts
# and update WHATSAPP_NUMBER to your Egyptian number
# in international format without the + sign.
# Example: 201012345678
